    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken meticulous care of it, and it still drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
