    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that remains in absolute showroom condition. This car has been maintained with an obsessive level of care, kept exclusively in a climate-controlled garage and shielded from the elements. The exterior paint possesses a deep, mirror-like luster, free from stone chips, swirl marks, or even the slightest door ding. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, reflecting the factory-original precision. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, showing no signs of creasing or wear, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. All high-gloss trim pieces are scratch-free, and every electronic component\u2014from the infotainment system to the seat heaters\u2014functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is peerless. It features a comprehensive, documented service history with all maintenance performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage is as clean as the roof. For the buyer who demands perfection and a turn-key experience, this is the finest example currently on the market.",
      "price": 48500.0,
